STEP 1 — Spotify Developer Setup

2- Go to developer.spotify.com → Login
3- Click Dashboard → Create App
Fill in:
App Name     → Now Playing Bot
   Redirect URI → http://localhost:8888/callback
   APIs         → Web API

4- Click Settings → copy Client ID and Client Secret
